Todd Hanson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Todd_Hanson 0 Todd Hanson is an American writer and voice actor, notable for his work as a writer and editor at the parody newspaper The Onion. He also voices the character Dan Halen on the Adult Swim program Squidbillies.
